            "answer_text": "What's another way to say \"long time no see\"? \u2018Long time no see\u2019 is mocking what people thought American Indians said in broken English when greeting one another. You could try, \u2018Hi. It\u2019s been too long,\u2019 or, \u2018Haven\u2019t seen you for ages.\u2019 or \u2018How are you? It\u2019s been a while!\u2019 ",
